FAQ

Quick answers to the most common questions.

Do you really buy houses as-is?

Yes. You dont need to repair anything. Tell us whats going on and well price it accordingly.

How fast can you close?

As soon as the title work is ready. If you need more time, we can close later too.

Any fees or commissions?

No commissions. Were not listing your homewere making a direct offer.

What happens after I submit?

Well contact you to confirm a few details and then send an offer.

Do I have to accept the offer?

No. The offer is free and theres no obligation.

What areas do you buy in?

We buy in many markets. Submit your address and well confirm if we can help.
